{"tid":1364545,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳茂波：近期暴力事件影響港金融聲譽","createTime":"2019-07-25T11:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T05:15:35.000Z","uid":212626,"like":43,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"f8db74a0a0930d413bc5f0632b885e2c05869f93","tid":1364545,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:24:46.000Z","msg":"財政司司長陳茂波今日在記者會上，宣布委任余偉文為金管局總裁，將於10月1日生效。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波在記者會上表示，近兩個月社會運動甚至出現暴力事件，對金融聲譽造成影響，暫未見有資金大規模撤出香港，未來會與國際溝通多加解說，維護市場對香港信心，並呼籲社會停止暴力。<br />\n<br />\n金管局將於月底公布上半年金融數字，陳茂波說，不排除屆時有財富管理相關資小流走，但政府至今未有見到「去到一個需要警覺程度」。<br />\n<br />\n本港經濟增長動力受壓，陳茂波稱，月底會公布上半年經濟表現，屆時會一併檢視增長預測。<br />\n<br />\n另外，陳茂波又提到，過去兩個月事件影響一般人信心，對市民生活亦有影響，有商戶及餐廳反映生意轉差。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/hongkong/article/2200419/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F2200419%2F&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6b7zmW0KSjJ%2FkJHMgTQKA%2BU%3D&h=aa7f8000\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/hongkong/article/2200419/</a>"},{"pid":"77025cd83cfb50d23271b9847dcdfbbfab3b2350","tid":1364545,"uid":261885,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:26:06.000Z","msg":"好耐無見波叔"},{"pid":"93b2b5b30d33415fa9b7b01a904a61f50ab92061","tid":1364545,"uid":202730,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:26:19.000Z","msg":"膠都費事比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 回收仲好 唔撚比陳茂波"},{"pid":"9577602138b395cf502f5eb72ea5d2c2014b3dbb","tid":1364545,"uid":149306,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:26:34.000Z","msg":"4000蚊呢？"},{"pid":"777adbba5340611d2a17b35f1bed816594721290","tid":1364545,"uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"77025cd83cfb50d23271b9847dcdfbbfab3b2350","tid":1364545,"uid":261885,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:26:06.000Z","msg":"好耐無見波叔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:27:19.00